details.description:
Cakeable Cafe is a full-service coffee shop offering a selection of baked goods that customers have come to know and love from the Cakeable team, in addition to hot and iced drinks.
About Cakeable Charlotte, Inc.: Cakeable is a nonprofit workforce development program for adults who live with intellectual and developmental disabilities. We offer vocational training and opportunities in the Cakeable Bakery and the Cakeable Cafe.

raw_data.name: Cakeable Cafe
raw_data.full_address: 401 N Tryon St #106, Charlotte, NC 28202, United States

reviews_data.review_text: Really love the opportunities this business is giving to people!! Service is always quick. Coffee is always hot and the goodies are always great!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for the review, Vickie! We look forward to serving you in the future.

reviews_data.review_text: Skipable if u want more than tea.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi David, I'm sorry we didn't meet your expectations! Do you have specific feedback you can share regarding how we could have improved your experience?

reviews_data.review_text: Great coffee spot!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Glad you enjoy it, Justin! Thanks for the review.

reviews_data.review_text: A wonderful place that offers amazing baked goods.
reviews_data.owner_answer: So glad you enjoy it, Brian. We look forward to serving you again.

reviews_data.review_text: Unironically the best cold brew I’ve ever had.
reviews_data.owner_answer: We are unironically grateful for your business and your kind review. :)

reviews_data.review_text: Inclusive ,  great coffee and cookies!, an awesome experience! Thanks Cakeable Cafe !
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for the review, Maria! Hope you come by and visit us again.

reviews_data.review_text: The coffee is delicious and the staff is precious!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you Micki! Hope you come by again!

reviews_data.review_text:
Best coffee!
Wonderful staff!!!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you Joni!

reviews_data.review_text: Incredibly kind and amazing service! I HIGHLY recommend the Oreo brownie! If you are near by, definitely check it out!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks Tori! Yes, that brownie is the best. We look forward to serving you again.

reviews_data.review_text: I love Cakeable!  It’s my favorite boutique cafè.  I get my day started with them often and always leave with a smile.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks so much for the kind words, Nitra! We look forward to serving you again.

reviews_data.review_text: The location is great, the coffee is great, and the mission is noble. Why give your money to large corporate coffee shops when you can support your community and get a high quality product!
reviews_data.owner_answer: We completely agree, Michael! :) Thank you for the great review. We look forward to serving you again.

reviews_data.review_text: The vision and purpose of this bakery is amazing!! They are doing the great work we are set out to do!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for the kind words, Kenyatta! We look forward to serving you again.

reviews_data.review_text: Great atmosphere and mission! Stopped by their Grand Opening and what a neat spot! Coffee, tea, and other drinks options plus a delicious looking baked good offerings. Will be back regularly!
reviews_data.owner_answer: So glad you enjoyed it, Tim! We look forward to serving you in the future.

reviews_data.review_text: The staff is very friendly and warm
reviews_data.owner_answer: It was lovely to serve you Sarika. Thanks!

reviews_data.review_text: We stopped here on a walking food tour and tried the lemon muffin, chocolate chip cookie, and nitro cold brew. Everything was delicious and the coffee was so smooth, but the best part was the staff. The cafe is a vocational training program that hires and equips adults with intellectual and developmental disabilities and trains them to to join the workforce of whatever vocation they are interested in. The people are precious!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks so much for coming by, Regan! We’re so glad you enjoyed everything.

reviews_data.review_text: Beautiful shop, beautiful mission!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks so much, Tom!

reviews_data.review_text: They are very friendly and sweet every time I get a drink here. Love the coffee here, and nice place to catch up with friends / colleagues!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for the lovely review, Durga. We're so glad you enjoy the cafe!

reviews_data.review_text: We popped in for a delicious lemonade. The service and environment were positive. So glad we stumbled upon this cafe
reviews_data.owner_answer: We’re so glad you enjoyed it! Thanks for stopping by.

reviews_data.review_text: The treats are delicious! I also love they have gluten free options. Beautiful space, super convenient and appreciate the parking validation. Love this place!
reviews_data.owner_answer: We’re so glad you enjoyed it, Angela!

reviews_data.review_text: I absolutely love this place 💞 The service, food and drinks are heavenly
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for the review, Tracey!

reviews_data.review_text: Cakeable is a beautiful cafe with caring staff. The drink and pastries were delicious, and I love the model of employment. Ordering was easy and appreciated the parking being validated as well. Great experience and will definitely be back as often as I can!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for the kind review. Come back and see us!

reviews_data.review_text: Visited Cakeable Cafe for the first time and it won't be my last.  What an adorable place with the most beautiful, friendly staff.  The cafe latte was delicious and there are plenty of yummy treats.
reviews_data.owner_answer: So glad you enjoyed it, Chris!

reviews_data.review_text: An absolute delightful place to go. The staff are wonderful, kind, and have servant hearts. I got the matcha latte and energy bites and they were amazing! I will be going back.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for the gracious review, Julia!

reviews_data.review_text: Cakeable has absolutely delicious treats and wonderful coffee. The store is beautiful with a beautiful mission.... to provide educational and work experience for some pretty awesome people!  A visit to this very special store is highly recommended.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks so much for the kind words, Lisa. We look forward to serving you in the future!

reviews_data.review_text: An amazing new Cafe with great coffee and an even greater mission to serve!
As a parent of a young autistic adult, I love the potential Cakeable sees in our special people.  I loved my Lavender syrup coffee and pastries.  Thank you Cakeable!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Glen, thanks for visiting and believing in our mission!

reviews_data.review_text: Cakeable is a unique group of baristas serving up some delicious coffee with amazing pastries. Gluten free offering often available as well.
reviews_data.owner_answer: So glad you enjoy the treats, Kenny!

reviews_data.review_text: I have had several great experiences at Cakeable Uptown.  The food is very tasty,  the service is quick and fantastic and the space is clean and friendly.  Too bad I don't drink coffee!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank so much for visiting, Susan. Next time, try ordering a steamed or iced milk with flavor of your choice!

reviews_data.review_text: Beautiful cafe with beautiful people. Delicious drinks and treats… the Oreo brownie is AMAZING! Empower those with disabilities by checking out this cool new spot!
reviews_data.owner_answer: So glad you enjoy our baked goods and drinks, Michele! Thanks for coming by.

reviews_data.review_text: Lovely place! Go and visit!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Brennen, so glad you enjoyed it! Thanks for coming in.

reviews_data.review_text: Great experience at Cakeable—will definitely be going back for that oreo brownie and mocha latte!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: We look forward to your next visit, Christopher!

reviews_data.review_text: Had a great experience visiting the Cakeable Cafe for the first time! Coffee and breakfast cookie were awesome and the staff was welcoming and helpful. Love the mission and excited to go back and fill out the rest of my punch card!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks so much for visiting the cafe, Casey! We're thrilled you enjoyed your visit, and we look forward to serving you again soon.

reviews_data.review_text: This cafe combines a fantastic concept with exceptional coffee quality. Situated perfectly for a quick grab-and-go, it's an ideal pitstop on your way to work.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks so much for the great review and photos, Bhuvana!

reviews_data.review_text: So impressed with the Cakeable team and movement. Snacks and coffee were excellent. Easily one of the most happy and encouraging coffee shop environments I’ve ever seen.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Kyle, thank you for the great review. We're so glad you enjoyed the coffee, treats and environment! :)

reviews_data.review_text: The coffee was very good. The treats are incredible. The service was great. The team is absolutely amazing. Their mission, to provide jobs and training for those IDDs, is executed well. Would not get coffee anywhere else!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you Christopher! We are so thankful for wonderful customers like you. Thanks for your loyalty.

reviews_data.review_text: Great spot for a coffee or treat.  Everyone inside was so friendly and nice.  The peanut butter brownie was delicious.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for the review, Sam. I'm so glad you enjoyed the brownie!
